To understand this repository, you need to understand the concept of recursion, inside out, because most of the problems in this 
repository is solved using recursion.

The following links will help understand recursion inside out:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/717725/understanding-recursion
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/14355629/recursion-in-c-understand-recursion-example
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/15941818/java-understanding-recursion
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/17745148/i-dont-understand-recursion
